OL,7,FShe added: "I remember when we went to
OL,8,FFrance, that wasn't planned - we fled
OL,9,Fbecause we couldn't afford the last
OL,10,Fpayment.
OL,12,F"I was given two days notice and I got
OL,13,Fdragged to France and I couldn't speak
OL,14,Fto mum and dad at home because dad's
OL,15,Fmental health was deteriorating - mum
OL,16,Fdidn't have a husband so their
OL,17,Frelationship was really bad and I'd
OL,18,Feither get shouted at or cried at.
